{"type": "article", "id": 23965, "title": "因为这些时髦的便当盒，你可能就愿意带便当上班了", "description": "男女通用，实用且酷", "date": "2016-03-16T15:11:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 15548, "name": "便当"}], "category": 17, "author": 474100, "comment_count": 37, "praise_count": 472, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702123436LX8GdzAU0ITrythl.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>作为一名上班族，午饭可以说是一天中相当重要的一部分。既要吃得营养健康还要保持美味优雅，当然你也希望便当盒最好是又萌又美，提起来能吸引眼球的那种。这里有一些看起来不那么像便当盒的盒子，款式简单大方，最要紧的是功能性还不错。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123432FjB7qIC6kdNUOlPg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123432tfOyskRNrYQgp6AW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123433RLV01nx5DUrBdiT7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>“Ojue”是一款手提式便当盒，它的独特之处像公文包一样扁平细长。Ojue 的宽度大约是 6 cm，可以分解成 3 个长盒子和 1 个筷子盒，携带时只要沿着侧面凹槽用橡皮筋固定一圈即可。能够根据饭量调整盒子数量，橡皮筋的长度也能随意调节。</p>\n<p>盒子整体密封性好，各个部分不会串味。要是把它和笔记本或参考书一起放在书包里，从侧面压根分辨不出哪个是你的便当盒。<a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/METAPHYS-%E3%83%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%83%81%E3%83%9C%E3%83%83%E3%82%AF%E3%82%B9-ojue%E7%AE%B8%E4%BB%98-P-63010/dp/B003ULHNC4%3FSubscriptionId%3DAKIAJBYZR3GMZFSHEFNQ%26tag%3Dnaver1-22%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB003ULHNC4\">可以在这里买到。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123433SrTuMbXnf2glVzcE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56210526\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123434NCOWsLVgiQSkb4JP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.572\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021234348DAJlaOCqUMexWT4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">“Prepd Pack”是个和 ipad 一样大的便当盒，比较适合男性，夹在胳膊底下隐约透着股酷劲儿。展开时饭盒变成一个自带的餐桌垫，省去饭后擦桌子这一步。要是你不知道每天带什么饭好，可以下载专门为这个饭盒提供食谱的 APP，各种食谱都和餐盒容量完美匹配。最近刚结束众筹，预计不久之后开始贩卖。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123435LWBUrHc6FDvjl7EY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123435dGUkhr8R4uyPs0gp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123436G1aebBkM3DxpPjo9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>“Compleat Foodskin”专为三明治设计，如果你要带着自己做的三明治上班，这个便携式手包是个不错的选择。这款盒子外壳弹性极大，水果或各种糕点都能装下。</p>\n<p class=\"\">题图来自 <a target=\"_blank\" jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" href=\"https://www.google.co.jp/url?sa=i&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=imgres&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=0ahUKEwj-18-G2MTLAhWHVZQKHX1iDZ8QjB0IBg&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.engadget.com%2F2016%2F01%2F19%2Fprepd-pack-lunchbox-healthkit%2F&amp;psig=AFQjCNGQsXzF8HbG1MFB8Tu36qzvSYteBg&amp;ust=1458199892696953\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwj-18-G2MTLAhWHVZQKHX1iDZ8QjB0IBg\" data-href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2016/01/19/prepd-pack-lunchbox-healthkit/\">engadget</a><br></p>\n<p class=\"\">内文图来自 <a href=\"http://mashable.com/2016/01/19/prepd-lunch-box/#uzcAkTWGjZqW\">mashable</a> <a href=\"http://kaden.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/column_review/yajreview/20101125_408856.html\">kaden</a></p>\n\n\n"}